Scope. This license covers the original work in this repository authored by
Jussi Alanärä: the A4091 driver sources (src/*.c), the host-side tooling
(tools/*), the SCSI SCRIPTS sources (reference/scripts/*), the kernel-patch
diffs (src/kernel-patches/*.patch) and the documentation.

The kernel-patch diffs are applied against Amiga UNIX (Amix), which is
proprietary Commodore/AT&T software and is NOT included or licensed here; you
must supply your own legally-obtained Amix. The A4091 autoboot ROM and the
ncr53cxxx SCRIPTS assembler come from the open-source a4091-software project
and carry their own licenses. See README.md ("Legal").
